13. Qh5 {We'd rather take with the queen on h7 than with the bishop.} 
13. Bxg5 {13...h614.Qg6doesn't change anything.} 
14. Qxh7+ {Now we go hunting for the king!} 
14. Kf7
15. Bg6+
15. Kf6
16. Bh5 {Black can only parry the mating threat on g6 with a great loss of material.} 
