7. d5 {The first knight must move.} 
7. Na5 {This is indeed the most popular move, but the saying 'A knight on the rim is dim' will definitely come true.} 
8. Bd3 {After the bishop's retreat, we are already threatening to win the stranded knight with b2-b4. Black is in a precarious position.} 
