6. Bg4 {6...Bf57.Ne5transposes to the line 5...Bf5 6. Ne5 c6.} 
7. h3 {Our reaction to the move ...Bg4 in the Scandinavian is always the same!} 
7. Bxf3
8. Qxf3
8. e6
9. Bd2 {We play O-O-O next and are clearly better thanks to the pair of bishops and the space advantage in the center.} 
