9. g4 {We play g2-g4 first so Black can't block us with h7-h5. Next we open the h-file with h2-h4-h5 and attack the black king. If necessary, we can try exchanging the important defender on g7 with Be3-h6. We have wonderful attacking prospects and are clearly in a better position.} 
