14. Kb6
15. Bxd6 {We have now regained a piece and the attack continues. The double check Bd6-c5+ followed by Nd3+ is in the air.} 
15. cxd6
16. Qxd6+
16. Ka5
17. Nd5 {If at all, Black can only fend off the mating attack with a large loss of material.} 
